jsl.observers.variable
Class WelchDataCollector

java.lang.Object
  jsl.observers.ModelElementObserver
      jsl.observers.variable.WelchDataCollector
All Implemented Interfaces:
ObserverIfc, IdentityIfc
public class WelchDataCollector
extends ModelElementObserver

Collects Welch data for a particular ResponseVariable (each observation for each replication) The data is stored in an array. There are memory implications if there are a large number of observations. The user specifies the maximum number of observations to be collected for each replication. If observations are not available, then the values will be Double.NaN

Author:
rossetti
